?BMX Query State Bitmap Extended Command. Get the current bitmap name+ justification for one or all indexes.
Syntax:
"'?BMX-<vt addr range>,<button states range>,[index]'"
Variables:
variable text address range = 1 - 4000.
button states range = 1 - 256 for multi-state buttons (0 = All states, for General buttons 1 = Off state and 2 =
On state).
Optional index = 0 - 5 The index of the bitmap to query. If not specified then all valid indexes are returned.
The response returned is a series of custom events (one for each valid index) with the following syntax:
Custom.ID = Button Address Code
